body:
Riot employee 1: &quot;hey steve do u think we should put odyssey on the pbe before releasing it?&quot;

riot employee 2: &quot;u and ur crazy ideas kevin why would we do that?&quot;

riot employee 1: &quot;maybe there could be some bugs and on the pbe its alright since the testserver is there to discover them&quot;

riot employee 2: &quot;maybe but imagine if we instead instantly release it 2 days after the announcement. the hype will be real&quot;

riot employee 1: &quot;but steve what if they are some kinda gamebreaking bugs?&quot;

riot employee 2: &quot;what are u thinking about? we never have major bugs after releasing new stuff&quot;

riot employee 3: &quot;yo guys what are u talking about?&quot;

riot employee 1&amp;2: &quot;possible bugs if we release odyssey without testing it&quot;

riot employee 3: &quot;i mean whjat could possibly happen. maybe the missions wont work. or players are stuck in intro and even if they win it they cant go into the harder modes cause the game does not realize that they won intro.&quot;

riot employee 1: &quot;uh jerry that would be kinda problematic. the players will be angry if stuff like that happens&quot;

riot employee 3:&quot;first of all my name is not jerry... and second they will be more occupied with buying the new skins and trying to equip augments which will also not work since the window wont load&quot;

riot employee 1: &quot;sorry u have such a forgettable face. is it bobby then?&quot;

riot employee 2: &quot;guys that doesnt mater right now. and steve his name is jimmy.&quot;

riot employee 4: &quot;guys guys what if somehow shit hits the fan so hard that people cant play ranked since the game thinks they own no champions?&quot;

riot employee 1, 2 &amp; 3: &quot;stacy dont be ridiculus even we cant fuck up that hard&quot;

[shit hit the fan](https://www.pic-upload.de/view-35944225/Unbenannt.png.html)
